      "title": "ElizaOS Discord Community Activity - May 12, 2026",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "In the general discussion channel, a developer named Ginga introduced themselves as a builder of AI and full-stack systems, emphasizing practical software delivery over hype, with a focus on clean, maintainable, and secure production-ready systems. The introduction received a positive reaction from the community. Separately, a user named DON DADA greeted the channel and asked if anyone needed chatters.",
